### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### ACCOUNTS
### Base: {{baseUrl}}/accounts
### Admin endpoints require X-Admin-Key header
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


### List all accounts (with embedded roles)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Accept: application/json

> {%
  // Auto-capture first account ID for use in other requests
  var accounts = response.body;
  if (accounts.length > 0) {
    client.global.set("accountId", accounts[0].id);
    client.log("Captured accountId: " + accounts[0].id);
  }
%}


###


### Create account with roles (admin only)
# Note: Use 02-admin.http → POST /admin/accounts-with-roles instead.
# Standalone account creation was removed; roles must be created together.


###


### Delete an account (admin only)
# Replace {{accountId}} with an actual UUID from the list above
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}
